---
<section id="programs" class="reveal mt-3 sm:mt-5 rounded-4xl sm:rounded-5xl bg-paper px-6 sm:px-12 py-14 sm:py-20" data-carousel>
  <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <span class="text-[12px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-emerald-light">Programs</span>
      <h2 class="h-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl mt-3">Built around <span class="accent">your</span> team</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden sm:flex gap-2">
      <button data-prev class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full ring-gold flex items-center justify-center text-inkt hover:bg-ink hover:text-white transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5M11 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg></button>
      <button data-next class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full ring-gold flex items-center justify-center text-inkt hover:bg-ink hover:text-white transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="car" data-track>
    <a href="#contact" class="car-card group block rounded-4xl overflow-hidden bg-white ring-1 ring-inkt/8">
      <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1543269865-cbf427effbad?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Team workshops"><span class="absolute top-4 left-4 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider bg-white/90 text-inkt rounded-full px-3 py-1">Most booked</span></div>
      <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Sales Team Workshops</h3><p class="mt-2 text-[14px] text-inkt/55">Role-play driven sessions, on-site or virtual.</p></div>
    </a>
    <a href="#contact" class="car-card group block rounded-4xl overflow-hidden bg-white ring-1 ring-inkt/8">
      <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="1-on-1 coaching"></div>
      <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium">1-on-1 Coaching</h3><p class="mt-2 text-[14px] text-inkt/55">Private weekly coaching for reps and leaders.</p></div>
    </a>
    <a href="#contact" class="car-card group block rounded-4xl overflow-hidden bg-white ring-1 ring-inkt/8">
      <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Leadership"></div>
      <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Sales Leadership</h3><p class="mt-2 text-[14px] text-inkt/55">Coach deals, forecast, build a winning culture.</p></div>
    </a>
    <a href="#contact" class="car-card group block rounded-4xl overflow-hidden bg-white ring-1 ring-inkt/8">
      <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1475721027785-f74eccf877e2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Keynotes"></div>
      <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Keynotes &amp; Kickoffs</h3><p class="mt-2 text-[14px] text-inkt/55">High-energy talks for kickoffs and conferences.</p></div>
    </a>
    <a href="#contact" class="car-card group block rounded-4xl overflow-hidden bg-white ring-1 ring-inkt/8">
      <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img class="zoomimg w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-b413da4baf72?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Virtual"></div>
      <div class="p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-medium">New-Hire Ramp</h3><p class="mt-2 text-[14px] text-inkt/55">Get new reps to quota in weeks, not months.</p></div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
